'''3C 58'''或'''3C58'''是在[[銀河系|銀河系]]中的[[脈衝星|脈衝星]]（正式名稱為PSR J0205+6449）和[[超新星殘骸|超新星殘骸]]（[[脈衝星風雲|脈衝星風雲]]），有人認為它可能與1181年的超新星[[SN_1181|SN 1181]]有關。然而，有跡象表明它已經有幾千年的歷史，因此與那顆超新星無關<ref>{{Cite journal|title = Radio Images of 3C 58: Expansion and Motion of Its Wisp|url = http://cdsbib.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/cdsbib?2006ApJ...645.1180B|journal = The Astrophysical Journal|date =2006-07-01 |issn = 0004-637X|pages = 1180–1187|volume = 645|doi = 10.1086/504584|first = M. F.|last = Bietenholz|s2cid = 16820726|issue = 2|arxiv = astro-ph/0603197 |bibcode = 2006ApJ...645.1180B }}</ref>。該天體最早列在[[3C星表|劍橋大學電波星表第三版]]，序號為58。

這顆脈衝星以其非常高的冷卻速率而引人注目，而[[中子星|中子星]]形成的標準理論無法解釋這一點。據推測，恆星內部的極端條件會導致高[[微中子|微中子]][[通量|通量]]，從而帶走能量，冷卻恆星<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2004/3c58/ |title=Chandra :: Photo Album :: 3C58 |publisher=Chandra.harvard.edu |date=2004-12-14 |accessdate=2012-08-21 |archive-date=2011-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110709021527/http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2004/3c58/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="yakovlev"/>。3C 58已經被提出可能是[[夸克星|夸克星]]<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.npl.washington.edu/AV/altvw114.html|title = Quark Stars|last = Cramer|first = John G.|date = November 2002|work = Analog Science Fiction & Fact Magazine|accessdate = 2015-08-17|via = |archive-date = 2010-12-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101217134156/http://www.npl.washington.edu/AV/altvw114.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = RX J1856.5-3754 (and the 3C58 Pulsar)|url = http://www.solstation.com/x-objects/rxj1856.htm|website = www.solstation.com|accessdate = 2015-08-18|archive-date = 2020-02-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200201143439/http://www.solstation.com/x-objects/rxj1856.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

它位於[[閣道二|閣道二]]（仙后座ε）東北方 2°，估計距離約10,000[[光年|光年]]。它的轉週期為65.7[[毫秒|ms]]，因此它屬於[[毫秒脈衝星|毫秒脈衝星]]。

